{"title":"断壁（外一首）","authors":["黄恩智"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":2,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"断壁（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄恩智"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一柄青铜剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被悠悠的岁月截断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日火依然在冶炼着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日光仍为它镀亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还剑的锋刃吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象在锤打着渴望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风在磨砺着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨在淬火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许亿万斯年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑的威赫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会挑起一切伫望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真的，这决不是梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猎　归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从空谷中走出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空空的双筒猎枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑着你的晦气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪口瞪着圆圆的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊愕着远去的野山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你沉默如哑人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几只山雀子掠过头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衔走了你进山狩猎的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山，层层叠叠的大山很空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你开始怨恨猎村怨恨自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和所有喝过兽血的猎人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤独的小路牵着孤独的你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步很沉，思绪很沉"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}